'''Ali Mohammed Lajami''' ({{langx|ar|علي محمد لاجامي}}; born 24 April 1996) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al Hilal FC|Al-Hilal]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Ali Lajami |url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/news-cristiano-ronaldo-s-al-nassr-dealt-blow-saudi-player-squad-joins-rivals-al-hilal |access-date=27 May 2025 |archive-date=22 January 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122025314/https://www.goalzz.com/main.aspx?player=109146 |url-status=live }}</ref> and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]]. {{as of|August 2024|post=,}} his twin brother [[Qassem Lajami]] also plays as a defender for Saudi Pro league side [[Al Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.arabnews.com/node/2361876/amp|title=How Saudi football twins became overnight social media stars|publisher=Arab News|date=26 August 2023|archive-date=9 March 2024|access-date=9 March 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240309070828/https://www.arabnews.com/node/2361876/amp|url-status=live}}</ref>

==Career==
Lajami began his career at the youth teams of [[Al-Muheet SC|Al-Muheet]]. On 29 July 2014, Lajami and his twin brother, [[Qassem Lajami|Qassem]], both joined [[Al-Khaleej FC|Al-Khaleej]].<ref>{{cite web |title=الخليج يدعم فريقه بتوأم المحيط |url=https://makkahnewspaper.com/article/50339/%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%8A-%D8%A2%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86---%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%87%D8%A7%D8%AA}}</ref> He made his debut on the last matchday of the 2014–15 season as a substitute in a 4–4 draw against [[Al-Taawoun FC|Al-Taawoun]]. On 24 July 2018, Lajami joined [[Al-Fateh SC|Al-Fateh]] on a four-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=نادي الفتح يتعاقد مع علي لاجامي و سلطان الدعيع |url=https://www.akhbaar24.com/article/detail/405009}}</ref> On 9 September 2020, Lajami joined [[Al-Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]] on a five-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=رسمياً.. "النصر" يتعاقد مع مدافع "الفتح" علي لاجامي لخمسة أعوام |url=https://sabq.org/38tb7v}}</ref> On 27 May 2025, Lajami joined derby rivals [[Al Hilal SFC|Al-Hilal]] on a free transfer.<ref>{{cite web |title=في صفقة انتقال حُر.. نادي الهلال يعلن التعاقد مع مدافع النصر "علي لاجامي" |url=https://sabq.org/sports/cmcf30fldt}}</ref>

